      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、本当にいろいろありましたけど\nなんとか、本番に間に合いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ there were really a lot of things going on‚\nbut somehow‚ I made it in time for the performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ミクと握手会に出たり、作詞も初めてで大変だったけど\n何もかもが新鮮で、楽しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku and I joined the greeting event and wrote lyrics. It was tough‚\nbut everything was fresh and enjoyable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その全てが、今日のステージのためだ\n期待してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everything you've been through was for today's stage.\nI'm expecting great things from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
